"Yeah, I'm ... just fine," Phoenix says, looking around.  "This is a 
little embarrassing, but I feel like I should know you; I lost a lot 
of memory engrams ..."  She scratches the back of her head - one of 
the few parts of her body that isn't marked somehow.
